## Download
```bash
pip install lgbt
```

## Usage
```python
import time

from lgbt import lgbt

for i in lgbt(range(100)):
	time.sleep(0.1)

# With update
bar = lgbt(total=100) # Necessary argument

for i in range(100):
	time.sleep(0.1)
	bar.update(1)

```

